channel.title: Turtlescape v2 The last of moparscape!
channel.description:
[size=36pt]TURTLESCAPE[/size]
[size=24pt]Creditis[/size]
Me iz3 legend Mod Allstar Moparscape
[size=36pt]A Short Summary![/size] [size=18pt]Turtlescape was based on an Old Moparscape Server which i tried to recreate. I know i have released v1 only 2 days ago but i have finished my server (as far as im willing to go.) Im going to try to move onto Shards/Hyperion which will be rough to be familiar with them.[/size]
[size=14pt]I have seen 3 people hosting this server which was a really cool thing. But they found a few glitches that i repaired for v2. This has been a fun server to code because i never took it as a serious development just a fun project. I learned a little but it was pretty much all based off prior knowledge. Yet im better with delta. but although, i have never released any Pi's im very good with them. When it comes to pi's i just dont think the world needs another one released.[/size]
[size=24pt]Combat[/size]
[size=12pt]Flawless DDS on a oldschool is pretty cool. Accurate hit formulas and no delay between specs.[/size]
[size=12pt]Edited the meat tenderiser changed the emotes and delays and all that good stuff.[/size]
[size=12pt]Amazing Switching![/size]
[size=12pt]Spent awhile on Granite maul but couldnt seem to get it you can finish it off[/size]
[size=12pt]Dharocks or however u spell it hits up to 75 now.[/size]
[size=12pt]Dds Switching 100%[/size]
[size=10pt]Dhally spec delay was removed and hit formulas where tweaked so they where more realiztic.[/size]
[size=12pt]Added P Ring for staff in staff zone :)[/size]
[size=12pt]Added a New combat shop[/size]
[size=36pt]Areas[/size]
[size=12pt]Cleaned out varrock bank looks alot better in my opinion not overflowing with objects so alot of room to trade.[/size]
[size=12pt]Moved all objects from v1 inside training house (looks very organized)[/size]
[size=12pt]Pimped out the pkbox looks really cool now and not so empty.[/size]
[size=12pt]Added 3 more chests to the staff zone with more items to obtain.[/size]
[size=12pt]Added Safe Zones in the correct spots.[/size]
[size=12pt]Left chickens and rats the same as v1 because i ran out of ideas.[/size]
[size=12pt]Added Food chest at pk box click it to get 100 manta rays.[/size]
[size=12pt]Added Cheerleaders at home saying text.[/size]
[size=12pt]added all teleports to the ancient mage book too.[/size]
[size=12pt]removed uneeded text interfaces (most of them)[/size]
[size=36pt]Pictures And Gif's[/size]
[size=12pt]Gif 1 Perfect DDS Rushing![/size]
[URL=http://tinypic.com/r/9pubgj/7]View My Video[/URL]
[URL=http://tinypic.com/r/2ppikci/7]View My Video[/URL]
[size=12pt]PICTURES![/size]
